    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study to assess post ablation, if there are areas of Barrett's mucosa
      post ablation and to assess the ability of the Fujinon FICE system to detect this, as
      compared to white light endoscopy. A subgroup will also be compared with laser confocal
      microscopy
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
